01:52:33.230 --> 01:52:34.230
Alex!

01:52:34.230 --> 01:52:37.230
The chlorine! Use the chlorine!

01:52:37.230 --> 01:53:34.400
Looks like he had control of me.

01:53:34.400 --> 01:53:36.400
I know.

01:53:36.400 --> 01:53:38.400
But how did you know the chlorine would stop him?

01:53:38.400 --> 01:53:44.060
He was on Crenshaw's chemistry exam.

01:53:44.060 --> 01:53:47.060
Chlorine kills bacteria and the leaves were organic,

01:53:47.060 --> 01:53:50.060
so I figured it would zap him.

01:53:50.060 --> 01:53:53.260
So it was right.

01:53:53.260 --> 01:54:01.630
Yeah, I guess you were.

01:54:01.630 --> 01:54:45.200
Welcome back.

01:54:45.200 --> 01:54:48.480
I'm afraid we failed.

01:54:48.480 --> 01:54:52.480
But I planted jewels in high schools all over the country.

01:54:52.480 --> 01:54:55.480
We'll have another chance.

01:54:55.480 --> 01:54:58.480
And to think, when I was a young girl,

01:54:58.480 --> 01:55:01.480
they thought I was mad.

01:55:10.480 --> 01:55:12.480
The end.

01:55:12.480 --> 01:55:14.480
I smell a sequel.

01:55:14.480 --> 01:55:15.480
Yeah.

01:55:15.480 --> 01:55:17.480
World's doomed.

01:55:17.480 --> 01:55:20.480
Well, on that cheerful note,

01:55:20.480 --> 01:55:23.480
I declare this meeting of the Midnight Society closed.

01:55:23.480 --> 01:56:13.860
We snicked. They will have snicked.

01:56:13.860 --> 01:56:15.860
It is post-snick.

01:56:15.860 --> 01:56:18.860
You can sneak again next Saturday night on Nickelodeon.

